OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Ffine end to the day with plenty of
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells, some
OL,9,Fpatchy cloud and light winds. A cool
OL,10,Fnight for many particularly in rural
OL,11,Fareas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FBlue skies at first, before a
OL,14,Flittle cloud bubbles up through the
OL,15,Fmorning. Still plenty of sunny spells
OL,16,Fand feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
